            <title><![CDATA[上海官方：目前没有封城也不必封城]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-03/file7k45t3lle8wndnth2bb.jpg?itok=D2hwKvf4" title="上海市黄浦区卢湾体育场临时核酸检测点昨天启用。（中新社）" alt="上海市黄浦区卢湾体育场临时核酸检测点昨天启用。（中新社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-03/file7k45t3lle8wndnth2bb.jpg?itok=D2hwKvf4" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
